Serialized Form

  • Package org.springcorebankapp.account

    • Class org.springcorebankapp.account.Account

      class Account extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • id
          int id
          Unique identifier for the account.

          This field is the primary key in the "accounts" table and is automatically generated using the IDENTITY strategy.

        • moneyAmount
          int moneyAmount
          The monetary balance currently held in the account.

          Maps to the "money_amount" column in the "accounts" table and represents the amount of funds available in the account.

        • userId
          int userId
          Identifier of the user who owns the account.

          Maps to the "user_id" column in the "accounts" table. This serves as a foreign key to link accounts to users.

  • Package org.springcorebankapp.user

    • Class org.springcorebankapp.user.User

      class User extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • accountList
          List<Account> accountList
          A list of accounts associated with the user. This is a one-to-many relationship, with cascade operations and orphan removal enabled. Accounts are lazily loaded when accessed.
        • id
          int id
          The unique identifier for a user. This field is auto-generated by the database as an identity column.
        • login
          String login
          The login of the user. This field is non-nullable and must be unique across all users.
